from maridai marida ignacio subject re every lent he suffer to save u the story i relate be one of the seven apparition approve by my church a worthy of belief it happen in la salle france the moral lesson of the story be the lamb of god ha be sacrifice and hi blood ha be use to cleanse u of my sin every moment a god perceife worthy of be do in heaven mary weep for the lamb and for the rest of her offspring thi will continue while we disobey god or sin against him mary a a messenger ha be give the task to make u be of the evil serpent communism war famine unfaithful disobedience to god etc run after the rest of her offspring the child who go astray by disobedience lead by the dragon be bring back by her peace and love message reparation for sin to obey god commandment and be more worthy to be in the presence of the lamb a she wa conceive without sin to be worthy of bear the son of god in her womb mary ha be prepare u the church the body of christ for hi second come make sure we be protect from the dragon also she ha be prepare the new eden by reverse the deed of the ancient eve the new eden will be the sanctuary of the righteou a judge by christ in hi next come i relate the story again i believe thi and mary in one of her apparition in or century she appear to these two child who tend goat and cow i forget the exact place she wa weep and tell the child that she be afraid she go to lose her son arm she be mourn too for these townfolk because it wa their fault that there would be drought in their harvest not much good food again thi year a it wa last year mary tell the child most of the townfolk in thi place work whole week even on sunday when they should be in church honor god these townfolk swear and use her son name in bad word that be why her son arm be so heavy in pain then she ask them if they pray the child say hardly she ask them to pray every morning and night when the child go back from work they have to tell somebody about thi when the news wa spred and after thorough investigation of the incident the townfolk be convert and faith and obedience to god be restore in their community once again the lamb succeed marida spread god word through action mother teresa 